body.paragraph: Inserts an empty list into a hole. The list can be populated with multiple values after creation by navigating inside the list and inserting a value. New values in a list are separated by a comma.
Lists can store a variety of types and even different types within the same list.

tooltip.title: Insert Editable List
tooltip.body: Inserts an empty list. Press comma before or after each item to add a new empty item.
